ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I highly recommend this course as it's really useful.
I would definitely recommend this course.
It was a good general overview of aquatic chemistry. I would say that if you are already comfortable with aquatic chemistry it is not necessary to take.
I would recommend this course to an environmental student or who is interested to deal with the aquatic problems.
This is a good course for students interesting in learning some of the basic concepts of aquatic chemistry.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course helps me understand quantitatively the complicated aquatic systems and teach me how to analyze it.
It helped to clarify and toconfirm my understanding of the topic.
This course provides certain knowledge for aquatic problems, which is helpful.
This help broaden my knowledge of the environmental engineering, which will be helpful as I strive to become an active member of this field.
